  "IsIntegrationProcedure": true,
  "Description": "Pre-Application Screening Integration Procedure. Guest-safe: reads NEPA_Permit_Matrix__mdt CMT only (no record DML). Accepts SectorKey, NAICSCode, LeadAgencyKey, ProjectDescription, and ProjectState. Calls the NEPA_CE_Screener BRE Expression Set for pathway classification, then overlays the Permit Matrix CMT row for RequiredPermits, AdjacentReviews, TypicalTimelineMonths, and EISLikelihoodPct. Called by NepaPreAppScreeningController (Agentforce action) and directly by the NEPA_PreApp_Screener OmniScript screening step.",
  "PropertySetConfig": "{\"persistentComponent\":true,\"trackingCustomData\":{},\"enableLWCRuntime\":true}",
  "WebComponentKey": "NEPA/PreApp_Screening_IP/English/1",
